hero.title: Australia Mus Championship 2026
hero.description: Ongi etorri! Are you ready to join us once again for the Australia Mus Championship? This year, the tournament will be held at Gure Txoko Sydney on June 13th. We will kick off at 11:00 AM and, as always, we'll enjoy an unbeatable atmosphere: intense matches, great food and drinks... and excitement until the very last card.
